We’d Love to Hear From You, Get In Touch With Us!The next time that you’re in need of sand and gravel in Los Angeles, look no further than us here at Western Materials. If you’ve driven past a public garden, baseball field, or construction crew laying road base in Los Angeles or Ventura County, odds are that the dirt, decorative stone or topsoil that you see came from us. Since 1999, we have provided many of our affiliated quarries throughout the state with quality construction aggregates and landscaping materials such as decomposed granite, wood chips, and class 2 base in Ventura.
Superior Materials and Services
Our team brings over 50 years of collective experience in supplying gravel and topsoil in Los Angeles and Ventura to every new job that we take on. Those companies, contractors, and private parties that we supply with aggregates and materials are more than just clients to us; they’re our partners in filling all of the needs for materials such as sand, road base, and wood chips in Los Angeles. From our founding members to our highly-qualified sales, production, and delivery teams, our philosophy has always remained to focus on the following business aspects:

Fielding a knowledgeable staff prepared to answer any question and fulfill any material and supply needs.
Demonstrating the care needed to not only meet, but exceed all of your expectations.
Fulfilling all of the regulatory requirements necessary to deliver on our company’s service guarantees.

We give you more than just road base in Ventura; we offer the peace-of-mind that comes from knowing your construction and landscaping projects are supported by the best materials in the business. Only through your satisfaction with your gravel in Los Angeles do we measure our success.











