            American DG Energy is an On-Site Utility that supplies electricity. The company serves clients in the commercial, institutional and industrial sectors. It sells and installs a variety of cogeneration and cooling systems. The company offers a range of financing options through third-party lending institutions. American DG Energy has received the Energy Star and EPA awards. It offers a selection of site evaluation, maintenance, engineering and design services. The company also offers equipment monitoring services 24 hours a day, seven days a week. It serves health care centers, sports complexes, educational institutions, residential facilities and detention centers. The company helps clients to get regulatory and permit approvals. American DG Energy analyzes the energy needs of its clients.
          






















